      <title>随着战争的加剧，以色列国防开支将攀升 80 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/israel-may-increase-defense-spending-by-8-billion-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据以色列财政部称，随着针对哈马斯的战争愈演愈烈，以色列明年将需要增加至少 300 亿谢克尔（83 亿美元）的国防开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/israel-may-increase-defense-spending-by-8-billion-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 14:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京敌人纳瓦尔尼在选举前转移到俄罗斯偏远监狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/putin-foe-navalny-moved-to-remote-russian-jail-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被监禁的俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼已被转移到偏远的北极监狱营地，结束了近三周他的盟友和律师都不知道他的下落的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/putin-foe-navalny-moved-to-remote-russian-jail-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 13:35:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称其击落了俄罗斯战斗机和无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/ukraine-says-it-shot-down-russian-fighter-jets-and-drones-as-the-country-officially-marks-christmas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰基辅（美联社）——乌克兰空军周一报告说，它在夜间击落了两架俄罗斯战斗机、两枚巡航导弹和 28 架沙赫德型无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/ukraine-says-it-shot-down-russian-fighter-jets-and-drones-as-the-country-officially-marks-christmas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 11:58:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教皇方济各在圣诞节呼吁全球和平时猛烈抨击武器工业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/pope-francis-blasts-the-weapons-industry-as-he-makes-a-christmas-appeal-for-peace-in-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马（美联社）——教皇方济各周一在圣诞节呼吁世界和平，特别是以色列和巴勒斯坦之间的和平，谴责武器工业及其助长战争的“死亡工具”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/pope-francis-blasts-the-weapons-industry-as-he-makes-a-christmas-appeal-for-peace-in-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 11:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡誓言扩大加沙战斗，埃及提出结束以色列与哈马斯战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/egypt-floats-ambitious-plan-to-end-israel-hamas-war-and-create-transitional-palestinian-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开罗（美联社）——埃及高级官员表示，埃及提出了一项雄心勃勃的初步建议，旨在通过停火、分阶段释放人质以及建立巴勒斯坦专家政府来结束以色列与哈马斯的战争，该政府将管理加沙地带和被占领的约旦河西岸一位欧洲外交官周一表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/egypt-floats-ambitious-plan-to-end-israel-hamas-war-and-create-transitional-palestinian-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 10:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因人口贩卖调查在法国滞留数日的飞机飞往印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/a-plane-stuck-for-days-in-france-for-a-human-trafficking-investigation-is-leaving-for-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国瓦特里（美联社）——当局称，一架因人口贩运调查而在法国停飞的包机于周一飞往印度，机上载有 276 名印度人。这些乘客原本打算前往尼加拉瓜，但却被困在法国乡村机场达四天之久，经历了一场特殊的假期磨难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/a-plane-stuck-for-days-in-france-for-a-human-trafficking-investigation-is-leaving-for-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 09:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>查理三世国王的圣诞致辞呼吁保护地球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/king-charles-iii-s-annual-christmas-message-from-buckingham-palace-includes-sustainable-touches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——查理三世国王周一在圣诞致辞中反映了他的加冕主题：公共服务，他将这一主题与地球的健康和正在肆虐的战争联系起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/king-charles-iii-s-annual-christmas-message-from-buckingham-palace-includes-sustainable-touches</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 05:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>平安夜科罗拉多购物中心发生枪击事件，造成 1 人死亡、3 人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/gunfire-erupts-at-a-colorado-mall-on-christmas-eve-one-man-is-dead-and-3-people-are-hurt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科罗拉多州科罗拉多斯普林斯（美联社）警方周日表示，平安夜科罗拉多州一家购物中心响起枪声，一名男子被枪杀，三人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/gunfire-erupts-at-a-colorado-mall-on-christmas-eve-one-man-is-dead-and-3-people-are-hurt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 04:13:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚总统武契奇在选举抗议暴力事件后敦促保持冷静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/serbia-protest-over-election-turns-violent-vucic-calls-for-calm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚首都的防暴警察使用胡椒喷雾击退了数千名试图冲击贝尔格莱德市政厅的抗议者，反对党和欧洲观察员称最近的选举存在违规行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/serbia-protest-over-election-turns-violent-vucic-calls-for-calm</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 20:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争中最致命的袭击之一导致加沙 68 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-24/a-weekend-of-combat-in-gaza-kills-more-than-a-dozen-israeli-soldiers-a-sign-of-hamas-entrenchment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙代尔巴拉赫（美联社）卫生官员周日表示，以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成至少 68 人死亡，周末在战斗中丧生的以色列士兵人数升至 17 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-24/a-weekend-of-combat-in-gaza-kills-more-than-a-dozen-israeli-soldiers-a-sign-of-hamas-entrenchment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 08:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
